<template>
    <PageWithHeader :title="title" :icon="icon" :loading="loading" :fixed-footer="true">
        <template slot="content">
            <slot name="content"/>
        </template>
        <template slot="actionButton">
            <slot name="actionButton"/>
        </template>
        <template slot="footer">
            <slot name="actions"/>
        </template>
    </PageWithHeader>
</template>
<script>
    import PageWithHeader from './PageWithHeader.vue';

    export default {
        name      : 'PageWithHeaderAndActions',
        props     : {
            title: {
                type   : String,
                default: 'Default page'
            },
            icon: {
                type   : String
            },
            loading: {
                type   : Boolean
            }
        },
        components: {
            PageWithHeader
        }
    }
</script>
<style scoped>
</style>
